             to the shop; Mr. Shelley was in the shop as we entered the shop. She looked round and said</p>
               <p>"this is the shop."</p>
               <p>Cross Examination.</p>
               <p>Was Mr. Shelley within hearing of this? - He was not a yard from her when she said it. I asked him</p>
               <p>"whether he had ever seen that woman before?" He said</p>
               <p>"no not to his knowledge."</p>
               <p>Had 
               <persName id="t17810222-32-person388">
