                  </persName>
             then on the same dress that is described in the hand-bill? - She had on the cloak and every thing as described in the bill.</p>
               <p>To Mrs. Steward. Was the description of the hand-bill a true description of the dress in which 
               <persName id="t17810222-32-person389">
